HOW TO BUY

Create a Wallet

Download Tonkeeper or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktop users, download the google chrome extension by going to tonkeeper.com

Get Some TON

Have TON in your wallet to switch to $VICKY. If you don’t have any TON, you can buy directly on Tonkeeper, transfer from another wallet, or buy on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

Go to Ston.fi

Connect to Ston.fi. Go to Ston.fi in google chrome or on the browser inside your Tonkeeper app. Connect your wallet. Paste the $VICKY token address into Ston.fi, select Chase, and confirm. When Tonkeeper prompts you for a wallet signature, sign.

Swap SOL for $VICKY

Swap TON for $VICKY. We have ZERO taxes so you don’t need to worry about buying with a specific slippage, although you may need to use slippage during times of market volatility.
